lead_paragraph: LEEDS--Dalia. The Board and staff of NYJTL deeply mourn the passing of Dalia Leeds, our treasured friend. Our sympathy and deepest condolences to her beloved husband, Laurence, and the entire Leeds family. NYJTL Board and staff 1/3
